name: BEYOND THE WALL
description:
A landscape of things more distant than as far as the eye can see.
Truth is personal, formed from what we do every day and handed down from people before us. On the other hand, something that is out of the ordinary is odd and even wrong. 
Something wrong is the truth for others.  Everything has many sides and has its beauty.  The choice is ours, to spend our lives within a meager wall or take the risk to climb a tall lighthouse to see other things beyond the walls.
